            <title>[CASSANDRA-17801] NPE bug in streaming checking if SSTable is being repaired</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17801</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
